# Step 12 – Build Airflow UI Plugin

Create a new Airflow UI plugin page:

```
Resource Efficiency Dashboard
```

Features:

### DAG Ranking Table

Show DAG resource waste ranking.

Example:

```
DAG                  CPU Waste   Mem Waste   Score
--------------------------------------------------
feature_pipeline       71%        63%         4.2
daily_etl              55%        48%         3.1
training_pipeline      21%        17%         1.2
```

---

### Task Details Page

Display:

```
