Current Resources
CPU request: 4
Memory request: 8GB

Recommended Resources
CPU request: 1.5
Memory request: 3.5GB

CPU waste: 70%
Memory waste: 62%
```

---

### Copy Executor Config Button

Generate snippet:

```
