  "KubernetesExecutor": {
    "request_cpu": "1.5",
    "limit_cpu": "2",
    "request_memory": "3.5Gi",
    "limit_memory": "4Gi"
  }
}
```

---

# Step 13 – Performance Optimization

Only process **recently active tasks**.

Example:

```
tasks that ran within the last 7 days
```

This avoids expensive Prometheus queries.

